Townscaper - LittleFirstPerson mod - v0.8.0 by Digitalzombie
===========================================================

How to install:
===============
1. Download "Melon Loader" by LavaGang:
https://github.com/LavaGang/MelonLoader/releases/latest/

2. Start the MelonLoader.Installer.exe

2.1. Click "Select" and navigate to your Townscaper folder and select the Townscaper.exe (usually: C:\Program Files(x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Townscaper\Townscaper.exe)

2.2. Untick the "Latest" checkbox and choose version 0.4.3

2.3. Click install 

2.4. During the installation a "Mods" folder gets created it your game folder. MelonLoader does not(!) change any game files. 
	 You can uninstall anytime through the installer or by deleting the "version.dll" file.

3. Download the mod (latest release) from: https://github.com/DigitalzombieTLD/Townscaper-LittleFirstPerson/releases/latest/

4. Extract the all files from the "LittleFirstPerson_Release_0.8.0.zip" into your games Mods folder

5. Start the game! 


What does it do?
=================
Adds first person mode to the game. 


How to use?
=================
Controls:
F2 - Enter/Exit first person mode. You will be placed at the position of the mouse cursor
F3 - While in FPS mode: Toggle build mode to build your town while in first person

WASD - Basic movement
Space- Jump
Q - Zoom
Shift - Sprint


Known issues
=================
Jumping needs more more work!


